(249, 2, 3, 'There are 8 mango trees ln a straight line.\nThe distance between each mango tree\nwith other is 3 metres. What is the distance\nbetween the first and the eighth tree ?', '', 'top', '24m', '21 m', '30 m', '27 m', 'B', 48, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>(B)</b></p>&#10;&#10;<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Total No. of Mango Trees&#10;= 8</p>&#10;&#10;<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Distance between 2 Trees&#10;= 3 meters</p>&#10;&#10;<p class=\"MsoNormal\">.\'. Distance&#10;between the first and the eighth tree = 7 x 3 = 21 meters</p>', '', '', '', 4, '5', '', '2020-03-16 09:33:25', '2020-03-14 07:55:39', 1, 1),
