(434, 61, 56, 'A person crosses 600 m long street in 5 minutes. What is his speed in km Per hour?&#160;', '', 'top', '3.6', '7.2', '8.4', '10', 'B', 56, 'C', '<b>(B)</b>&#160;<div>$$\\begin{aligned}&#10;&amp;\\text { The person\'s speed }=\\frac{600 \\mathrm{m} \\times 60 \\mathrm{min}}{5 \\mathrm{min} \\times 1000 \\mathrm{m}} \\mathrm{km}\\\\&#10;&amp;=\\frac{36000}{5000}=7.2 \\mathrm{km}&#10;\\end{aligned}$$</div>', '', '0', '2020-03-16 00:00:00', '2020-03-16 00:00:00', 1),
(435, 61, 57, 'A man travelled 2/11 of his journey by coach,17/22 by rail and walked the remaining 1 km. How far did he go ?', '', 'top', '22 km', '20 km', '33 km', '27 km', 'A', 57, 'D', '<b>(A)</b>&#160;<div><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\">Let the distance covered by him be x km.</font></div><div><div>$$\\begin{aligned}&#10;&amp;\\therefore x-\\left(\\frac{2}{11} x+\\frac{17}{22} x\\right)=1 \\mathrm{km}\\\\&#10;&amp;x-\\left(\\frac{4 x+17 x}{22}\\right)=1 \\mathrm{km}\\\\&#10;&amp;x-\\frac{21}{22} x=1 \\mathrm{km}&#10;\\end{aligned}$$&#10;$$\\frac{22 x-21 x}{22}=1 \\mathrm{km}$$&#10;$$x=1 \\times 22=22 \\mathrm{km}$$&#10;&#8756; The distance he went = 22Km</div></div>', '', '0', '2020-03-16 00:00:00', '2020-03-16 00:00:00', 1),
(436, 61, 58, 'A ramp for unloading a moving truck has an angle of elevation of 30<span>&#730;</span>. If the top of the ramp is 0.9 m above the ground level then find the length of the ramp.', '', 'top', '2 m', '1.5 m', '1.8 m', '1.6 m', 'C', 58, 'C', '<b>(C)&#160;</b><div>&#160;In the figure, Ac is the ramp.&#10;Let the length of the ramp be \'l \' m&#10;$$\\begin{aligned}&#10;&amp;\\sin 30=\\frac{0.9}{1}\\\\&#10;&amp;\\frac{1}{2}=\\frac{0.9}{1}&#10;\\end{aligned}$$&#10;l=0.9 x 2m = 1.8m&#10;.\'. The length of the ramp = 1.8 m</div>', 'uploads/da593f1e3fb9c019d2d43fa18a64a9e8.jpg', 'top', '2020-03-16 00:00:00', '2020-03-16 00:00:00', 1),
