(503, 65, 72, 'The cost of levelling and turfing a square lawn at Rs.2.50 per&#160;<span>m</span><sup>2&#160;</sup>is Rs.13322.50. Find the cost of fencing if at Rs.5 per metre.', '', 'top', '&#8377;1,500.00', '&#8377;1,380.00', '&#8377;1,225.00', '&#8377;1,460.00', 'D', 72, 'A', '<b>&#10;(D)&#160;</b><div>The cost of leveling and turfing the square lawn = Rs.13322.50</div><div><div><div>$\\therefore$ Area of the square lawn $=$ Rs. $\\frac{13322.50}{2.50}$</div><div>$$<span>=\\frac{13322.5}{2.5}=5329 \\mathrm{m}^{2}</span><span>$$</span></div></div><div>$\\therefore$ Side of the square $=\\sqrt{5329}=73 \\mathrm{m}$</div></div><div>Perimeter of a square = 4a<br></div><div>Perimeter of the square lawn = 4 x 73 = 292 m</div><div><div>.\'.The cost of fencing the lawn = 292<span>&#160;x 5 = Rs. 1460</span></div></div>', '', '0', '2020-03-16 00:00:00', '2020-03-16 00:00:00', 1),
