(696, 101, 252, 'Work in a fort 300 men had provisions for\n90 days atler 20 days 50 men left the fort.\nHow long would the food last at the same rate?', '', 'top', '160 days', '210 days', '84 days', '80 days', 'C', 51, 'B', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>C)</b></p>&#10;&#10;<p class=\"MsoNormal\">After 20 days the food&#10;left is sufficient for 300 persons for 90-20 = 70 days</p>&#10;&#10;<p class=\"MsoNormal\">.\'. Remaining men =&#10;300-50 = 25O</p>&#10;&#10;<table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">&#10; <tbody><tr>&#10;  <td width=\"49\" valign=\"top\">&#10;  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">Men</p>&#10;  </td>&#10;  <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">&#10;  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">Days</p>&#10;  </td>&#10; </tr>&#10; <tr>&#10;  <td width=\"49\" valign=\"top\">&#10;  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">300</p>&#10;  </td>&#10;  <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">&#10;  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">70</p>&#10;  </td>&#10; </tr>&#10; <tr>&#10;  <td width=\"49\" valign=\"top\">&#10;  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">250</p>&#10;  </td>&#10;  <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">&#10;  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">?</p>&#10;  </td>&#10; </tr>&#10;</tbody></table>&#10;&#10;<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Food will be&#10;sufficient for $70 \\times \\frac{300}{250}$</p>&#10;&#10;<p class=\"MsoNormal\">$$=70 \\times \\frac{30}{25}$$<br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">$$=70 \\times \\frac{6}{5}=14 \\times 6=84 \\text { days }$$<br></p>', '', '', '2020-03-16 00:00:00', '2020-03-16 00:00:00', 1),
(697, 101, 259, '$$\\text { Simplify : }(1350 \\div 15-5) \\div(47.5-15 \\times 2.5)$$', '', 'top', '85', '10.5', '10', '8.5', 'D', 58, 'B', '<div><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\"><b>(D)</b></font></div><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\">$$(1350 \\div 15-5)=\\frac{1350}{15}-5=(90-5)=85$$</font><div><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\">$$(47.5-15 \\times 2.5)=(47.5-37.5)=10$$<br></font></div><div><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\">$$\\therefore(1350 \\div 15-5) \\div(47.5-15 \\times 2.5)$$<br></font></div><div><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\">$$=85 \\div 10=8.5$$<br></font></div>', '', '', '2020-03-16 00:00:00', '2020-03-16 00:00:00', 1),
