(787, 108, 257, '$$\\text { Simplify }: \\frac{x+3}{x^{3}-1} \\div \\frac{3 x+9}{x^{2}+x+1}$$', '', 'top', '$$\\frac{1}{3 x+1}$$', '3x + 1', '$$\\frac{1}{3 x-1}$$', '3x - 1', 'D', 56, 'C', '<font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\"><b>(D)</b></font><div><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\"><div>$\\left(x^{3}-1\\right)=(x-1)\\left(x^{2}+x+1\\right)$</div><div>$\\left(x^{2}+x+1\\right)=\\frac{\\left(x^{3}-1\\right)}{(x-1)}$</div><div>Given expression may be written as</div><div>$\\frac{(x+3)}{\\left(x^{3}-1\\right)} \\div \\frac{3(x+3)(x-1)}{\\left(x^{3}-1\\right)}$</div><div>(i.e) $\\frac{(x+3)}{(x-1)\\left(x^{2}+x+1\\right)} \\div \\frac{3(x+3)(x-1)}{(x-1)\\left(x^{2}+x+1\\right)}$</div><div>(i.e) $\\quad \\frac{(x+3)}{3(x+3)(x-1)}=\\frac{1}{3 x-3}$</div></font></div>', '', '', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', 1),
(788, 108, 258, 'Sasi purchased a house for&#160;<span>&#8377;</span>27,75,000&#10;and spent&#160;<span>&#8377;</span>2,25,000 on its interior&#10;decoration. He sold the house to make a&#10;profit of 40%. What is the selling price of&#10;the house ?', '', 'top', '<span>&#8377;</span>31,20,000', '<span>&#8377;</span>36,00,000', '<span>&#8377;</span>42,00,000', '<span>&#8377;</span>48,00,000', 'C', 57, 'D', '<font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\"><b>(C)</b></font><div><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\">Cost price of house = Rs.27,75,000<br></font></div><div><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\">Repair cost = Rs.2,25,000<br></font></div><div><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\">.\'. Total amount spent = Rs.30,00,000<br></font></div><div><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\">Profit = Rs.40%<br></font></div><div><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\">.\'. Selling price<br></font></div><div><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\">$$=\\left(30,00,000 \\times \\frac{40}{100}\\right)+30,00,000$$<br></font></div><div><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\">=Rs.(12,00,000 + 30,00,000)<br></font></div><div><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\">= Rs.42,00,000.<br></font></div>', '', '', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', 1),
(789, 108, 259, '$$\\text { Simplify : }(1350 \\div 15-5) \\div(47.5-15 \\times 2.5)$$', '', 'top', '85', '10.5', '10', '8.5', 'D', 58, 'C', '<div><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\"><b>(D)</b></font></div><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\">$$(1350 \\div 15-5)=\\frac{1350}{15}-5=(90-5)=85$$</font><div><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\">$$(47.5-15 \\times 2.5)=(47.5-37.5)=10$$<br></font></div><div><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\">$$\\therefore(1350 \\div 15-5) \\div(47.5-15 \\times 2.5)$$<br></font></div><div><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\">$$=85 \\div 10=8.5$$<br></font></div>', '', '', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', 1),
