(895, 108, 363, 'Raiu starts walking towards south. After\nwalking 20 m he turns towards North and\nWalks 8m. Again he turns towards East\nand walks 5m. How far and in which\ndirection is he from his starting point.', '', 'top', '15 m, South', '17 m, North-West', '7 m, East', '13 m, South-East', 'D', 161, 'C', '<font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\"><b>(D)</b></font><div><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\">.\'. AC = AB - CB<br></font></div><div><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\">&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;= 20 - 8 = 12</font></div><div><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\">$$\\mathrm{AD}=\\sqrt{\\mathrm{AC}^{2}+\\mathrm{CD}^{2}}$$<br></font></div><div><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\">$$=\\sqrt{12^{2}+5^{2}}=\\sqrt{144+25}=\\sqrt{169}$$<br></font></div><div><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\">.\'.AD = 13m<br></font></div><div><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\"><div>From the starting point Raju is in South-East&#160;<span>Direction.</span></div></font></div>', '', '', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', 1),
(896, 108, 364, 'The sides of 14 Square\'s are 1l cm, 12\ncrn, 13 cm ________ 24 cm, then find the\ntotal area of 14 squares.', '', 'top', '3515 cm2', '4515 cm2', '2715 cm2', '3215 cm2', 'B', 162, 'D', '<font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\"><b>(B)</b></font><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Area of Square = side x side</p>&#10;&#10;<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Total area of 14 squares = 11<sup>2</sup>+12<sup>2</sup>+13<sup>2</sup>+.....+24<sup>2</sup></p>&#10;&#10;<p class=\"MsoNormal\">= (1<sup>2</sup> +2<sup>2</sup> + &#8230;.... +24<sup>2</sup>) - (1<sup>2</sup>+2<sup>2</sup>+.....&#10;+ 10<sup>2</sup>)</p>&#10;&#10;<p class=\"MsoNormal\">$$=\\left(\\frac{24(25)(49)}{6}\\right)-\\left(\\frac{10(11)(21)}{6}\\right)$$</p>&#10;&#10;<p class=\"MsoNormal\">= (4900 - 385) cm<sup>2</sup></p>&#10;&#10;<p class=\"MsoNormal\">= 4515 cm<sup>2</sup></p></div>', '', '', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', 1),
