(1076, 126, 62, 'Shyam\'s monthly income is Rs.12,000. He saves Rs.1200. Find the percent of his savings and his expenditure', '', 'top', '10%,80%', '10%, 90%', '80%, 10%', '90%\' 10%', 'B', 62, 'D', '<table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"324\">&#10; <tbody><tr>&#10;  <td width=\"210\" valign=\"top\">&#10;  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br></p></td><td width=\"114\" colspan=\"2\"></td></tr><tr><td width=\"210\" valign=\"top\"><table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"324\">&#10; <tbody><tr>&#10;  <td width=\"210\" valign=\"top\">&#10;  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>(B)</b></p>&#10;  </td>&#10;  <td width=\"114\" colspan=\"2\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\">&#160;</p></td>&#10; </tr>&#10; <tr>&#10;  <td width=\"210\" valign=\"top\">&#10;  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">Shyam\'s monthly income</p>&#10;  </td>&#10;  <td width=\"24\" valign=\"top\">&#10;  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">=</p>&#10;  </td>&#10;  <td width=\"90\" valign=\"top\">&#10;  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">Rs. 12,000</p>&#10;  </td>&#10; </tr>&#10; <tr>&#10;  <td width=\"210\" valign=\"top\">&#10;  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">Savings</p>&#10;  </td>&#10;  <td width=\"24\" valign=\"top\">&#10;  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">=</p>&#10;  </td>&#10;  <td width=\"90\" valign=\"top\">&#10;  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">Rs.&#160; &#160;&#160;1200</p>&#10;  </td>&#10; </tr>&#10; <tr>&#10;  <td width=\"210\" valign=\"top\">&#10;  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; Expenditure</p>&#10;  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">&#160;&#160;&#160; &#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;</p>&#10;  </td>&#10;  <td width=\"24\" valign=\"top\">&#10;  <p class=\"MsoNormal