(1094, 126, 156, 'The students of a class donated &#8377;4624 for Chief&#10;Minister\'s State Relief Fund. Each student donated&#10;as many rupees as the number of students in the&#10;class. Find the number of students in the class.', '', 'top', '64', '68', '62', '78', 'B', 156, 'C', '<b>(B)</b>&#160;<div>Let the number of students in the class be = x&#160;</div><div>.\'. Amount donated by each student = Rs x&#160;</div><div><table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">&#10; <tbody><tr>&#10;  <td width=\"115\" valign=\"top\">&#10;  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">.\'. Total amount</p>&#10;  </td>&#10;  <td width=\"156\" colspan=\"2\" valign=\"top\">&#10;  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">= X X X</p>&#10;  </td>&#10; </tr>&#10; <tr>&#10;  <td width=\"115\" valign=\"top\">&#10;  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">&#160;</p>&#10;  </td>&#10;  <td width=\"156\" colspan=\"2\" valign=\"top\">&#10;  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">= 4624</p>&#10;  </td>&#10; </tr>&#10; <tr>&#10;  <td width=\"115\" valign=\"top\">&#10;  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; x<sup>2</sup> </p>&#10;  </td>&#10;  <td width=\"156\" colspan=\"2\" valign=\"top\">&#10;  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">= 4624</p>&#10;  </td>&#10; </tr>&#10; <tr>&#10;  <td width=\"271\" colspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\">&#10;  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">$$x=\\sqrt{4624}=68$$</p>&#10;  </td>&#10; </tr>&#10; <tr>&#10;  <td width=\"226\" colspan=\"2\" valign=\"top\">&#10;  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">.\'. the number is =68</p>&#10;  </td>&#10;  <td width=\"45\" valign=\"top\">&#10;  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br></p>&#10;  </td>&#10; </tr>&#10; &#10; <tr height=\"0\">&#10;  <td width=\"115\"></td>&#10;  <td width=\"111\"></td>&#10;  <td width=\"45\"></td>&#10; </tr>&#10; &#10;</tbody></table></div>', '', '0', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', 1),
(1095, 127, 54, 'In a right triangular ground, the sides adjacent to the right angle are 50 m and 80 m. Find the cost of cementing the ground at Rs.5/sq.m', '', 'top', '&#8377;20000', '&#8377;15000', '&#8377;10000', '&#8377;12500', 'C', 54, 'B', '<b>(C)</b>&#160;<div>In the right triangular ground ABC, AB becomes the height of the triangle&#160;</div><div>And BC becomes the base of the triangle.&#160;</div><div>Area of the triangle$$=\\frac{1}{2} \\times \\mathrm{AB} \\times \\mathrm{BC}=\\frac{1}{2} \\times 80 \\times 50=2000 \\mathrm{sq.m}$$&#160;</div><div>.\'. The cost of cementing ground @ Rs.5/sq.m.&#160;</div><div><span>&#160;2000 x 5 = Rs.10,000/-</span></div>', 'uploads/3c206566a40113c85e440734cd5b9f7e.jpg', 'top', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', 1),
