(1127, 128, 57, 'A man travelled 2/11 of his journey by coach,17/22 by rail and walked the remaining 1 km. How far did he go ?', '', 'top', '22 km', '20 km', '33 km', '27 km', 'A', 57, 'C', '<b>(A)</b>&#160;<div><font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\">Let the distance covered by him be x km.</font></div><div><div>$$\\begin{aligned}&#10;&amp;\\therefore x-\\left(\\frac{2}{11} x+\\frac{17}{22} x\\right)=1 \\mathrm{km}\\\\&#10;&amp;x-\\left(\\frac{4 x+17 x}{22}\\right)=1 \\mathrm{km}\\\\&#10;&amp;x-\\frac{21}{22} x=1 \\mathrm{km}&#10;\\end{aligned}$$&#10;$$\\frac{22 x-21 x}{22}=1 \\mathrm{km}$$&#10;$$x=1 \\times 22=22 \\mathrm{km}$$&#10;&#8756; The distance he went = 22Km</div></div>', '', '0', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', 1);
