(1230, 131, 70, 'Which one of the following cannot be the sides of a triangle ?', '', 'top', '4, 5, 6', '3, 4, 6', '2,<font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\"> </font>3, 4', '1,<font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\"> </font>2, 3', 'D', 70, 'B', '<b>(D)</b>&#160;<div>&#160;In a triangle, the sum of any two sides of it must be greater than the third side&#160;<div>&#160;A) 4, 5, 6 - triangle can be formed&#160;</div><div>&#160;B) 3, 4, 6 - triangle can be formed&#160;</div><div>&#160;C) 2,9,4 - triangle can be formed&#160;</div><div>&#160;D) 1,2,3 - 1+2=3;&#160;</div><div>&#160;Here the sum of the two sides is not&#160;<span>greater than the third side. A triangle</span></div><div>cannot be formed.</div><div>Hence the option (D) is the answer.<br></div></div>', '', '0', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', 1),
