(1254, 138, 65, 'If LCM of \"a\" and \"b\" is a and LCM of \"b\" and \"c\" is b. then what is the LCM of \"c\" and \"a\".', '', 'top', 'a', 'b', 'c', 'abc', 'A', 65, 'B', '<b>(A)</b><div>L.C.M of \'a\' and \'b\' = a&#160;<div>&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;a x b = a&#160;</div><div>$$b=\\frac{a}{a}=1$$&#160;</div><div>L.C.M of \'b\' and \'c\' = b</div><div>&#160;$$C=\\frac{b}{b}=1$$</div><div>.\'. L.C.M. of \'c&#8217; and \'a\'  =  1 x a = a</div></div>', '', '0', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', 1),
(1255, 138, 65, 'If LCM of \"a\" and \"b\" is a and LCM of \"b\" and \"c\" is b. then what is the LCM of \"c\" and \"a\".', '', 'top', 'a', 'b', 'c', 'abc', 'A', 65, 'B', '<b>(A)</b><div>L.C.M of \'a\' and \'b\' = a&#160;<div>&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;a x b = a&#160;</div><div>$$b=\\frac{a}{a}=1$$&#160;</div><div>L.C.M of \'b\' and \'c\' = b</div><div>&#160;$$C=\\frac{b}{b}=1$$</div><div>.\'. L.C.M. of \'c&#8217; and \'a\'  =  1 x a = a</div></div>', '', '0', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', 1),
(1256, 138, 66, 'Which one is correct ?', '', 'top', '$$\\frac{-3}{5}&lt;\\frac{-13}{40}&lt;\\frac{-15}{80}&lt;\\frac{-1}{20}&lt;\\frac{1}{2}$$<br>', '$$-\\frac{3}{5}&lt;\\frac{-1}{20}&lt;\\frac{-13}{40}&lt;\\frac{-15}{80}&lt;\\frac{1}{2}$$<br>', '$$-\\frac{3}{5}&lt;\\frac{-1}{20}&lt;\\frac{-13}{40}&lt;\\frac{-15}{80}&lt;\\frac{1}{2}$$<br>', '$$\\frac{1}{2}&lt;\\frac{-3}{5}&lt;\\frac{-1}{20}&lt;\\frac{-13}{40}&lt;\\frac{-15}{80}$$<br>', 'A', 66, 'B', '<div><b>(A)</b></div>$$\\text { A) } \\frac{-3}{5}&lt;\\frac{-13}{40}&lt;\\frac{-15}{80}&lt;\\frac{-1}{20}&lt;\\frac{1}{2}$$<br><div>$$=\\frac{-48&lt;-26-15&lt;-4&lt;40}{80}$$<br></div><div>$$=\\frac{-48&lt;-26&lt;15&lt;-4&lt;40}{80}$$<br></div><div>$$=\\frac{-48}{80}&lt;\\frac{-26}{80}&lt;\\frac{-15}{80}&lt;\\frac{-4}{80}&lt;\\frac{40}{80}$$<br></div><div>This is the correct order</div><div>&#160;Option (A) is correct.</div>', '', '0', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', 1),
(1257, 138, 70, 'Which one of the following cannot be the sides of a triangle ?', '', 'top', '4, 5, 6', '3, 4, 6', '2,<font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\"> </font>3, 4', '1,<font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\"> </font>2, 3', 'D', 70, 'B', '<b>(D)</b>&#160;<div>&#160;In a triangle, the sum of any two sides of it must be greater than the third side&#160;<div>&#160;A) 4, 5, 6 - triangle can be formed&#160;</div><div>&#160;B) 3, 4, 6 - triangle can be formed&#160;</div><div>&#160;C) 2,9,4 - triangle can be formed&#160;</div><div>&#160;D) 1,2,3 - 1+2=3;&#160;</div><div>&#160;Here the sum of the two sides is not&#160;<span>greater than the third side. A triangle</span></div><div>cannot be formed.</div><div>Hence the option (D) is the answer.<br></div></div>', '', '0', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', 1),
(1258, 138, 71, 'Without using logarithm table find approximate value for <span>log</span><sub>10</sub><span> 2.</span><br>', '', 'top', '0.2401', '0.3', '0.3802', '1.414', 'B', 71, 'B', '<font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\"><b>(B)</b></font><div><table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">&#10; <tbody><tr>&#10;  <td width=\"470\" valign=\"top\">&#10;  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>$$2^{10}=1024$$</span></p>&#10;  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>$$2^{10} \\sim 1000$$</span></p>&#10;  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>$$10 \\log _{10} 2 \\sim 3$$</span></p>&#10;  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>$$\\log _{10} 2 \\quad \\sim \\frac{3}{10}$$</span></p>&#10;  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>$$\\log _{10} 2 \\quad \\sim \\quad 0.3 \\text {&#10;  (approximately) }$$</span></p>&#10;  </td>&#10;  <td width=\"168\" valign=\"top\">&#10;  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>&#160;</span></p>&#10;  </td>&#10; </tr>&#10;</tbody></table></div>', '', '0', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', 1),
(1259, 138, 72, 'The cost of levelling and turfing a square lawn at Rs.2.50 per&#160;<span>m</span><sup>2&#160;</sup>is Rs.13322.50. Find the cost of fencing if at Rs.5 per metre.', '', 'top', '&#8377;1,500.00', '&#8377;1,380.00', '&#8377;1,225.00', '&#8377;1,460.00', 'D', 72, 'A', '<b>&#10;(D)&#160;</b><div>The cost of leveling and turfing the square lawn = Rs.13322.50</div><div><div><div>$\\therefore$ Area of the square lawn $=$ Rs. $\\frac{13322.50}{2.50}$</div><div>$$=\\frac{13322.5}{2.5}=5329 \\mathrm{m}^{2}$$<br></div></div><div>$\\therefore$ Side of the square $=\\sqrt{5329}=73 \\mathrm{m}$</div></div><div>Perimeter of a square = 4a<br></div><div>Perimeter of the square lawn = 4 x 73 = 292 m</div><div><div>.\'.The cost of fencing the lawn = 292<span>&#160;x 5 = Rs. 1460</span></div></div>', '', '0', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', 1),
