(1323, 140, 70, 'Which one of the following cannot be the sides of a triangle ?', '', 'top', '4, 5, 6', '3, 4, 6', '2,<font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\"> </font>3, 4', '1,<font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\"> </font>2, 3', 'D', 70, 'C', '<b>(D)</b>&#160;<div>&#160;In a triangle, the sum of any two sides of it must be greater than the third side&#160;<div>&#160;A) 4, 5, 6 - triangle can be formed&#160;</div><div>&#160;B) 3, 4, 6 - triangle can be formed&#160;</div><div>&#160;C) 2,9,4 - triangle can be formed&#160;</div><div>&#160;D) 1,2,3 - 1+2=3;&#160;</div><div>&#160;Here the sum of the two sides is not&#160;<span>greater than the third side. A triangle</span></div><div>cannot be formed.</div><div>Hence the option (D) is the answer.<br></div></div>', '', '0', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', 1),
(1324, 140, 73, 'The diameter of a semicircular grass plot is 70 m. Find the cost of fencing the plot at&#160; &#8377;12 per metre.', '', 'top', '&#8377;7,700.00', '&#8377;840.00', '&#8377;2,160.00', '&#8377;4,320.00', 'C', 73, 'B', '<b>(C)</b><div><b><br></b><div>Diameter of the semicircular plot (d) = 70 m&#160;<div>&#160;.\'. radius (r) = 35 m&#160;</div><div>circumference = 2<span>&#8719;r</span><br></div><div>$$Perimeter of semicircle = Diameter +\\frac{1}{2} \\times circumference$$<br></div><div><span>$$=70+\\frac{1}{2} \\times \\frac{22}{7} \\times 35 \\times 2=70+110=180 \\mathrm{m}$$<br></span></div><div>.\'. The cost of fencing the plot= 180<font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\"> </font>x 12<br></div><div><span>&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;= Rs. 2,160</span></div></div></div>', 'uploads/f918e655e6e9c8c351b7ca03306a0a13.jpg', 'top', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', 1),
(1325, 140, 72, 'The cost of levelling and turfing a square lawn at Rs.2.50 per&#160;<span>m</span><sup>2&#160;</sup>is Rs.13322.50. Find the cost of fencing if at Rs.5 per metre.', '', 'top', '&#8377;1,500.00', '&#8377;1,380.00', '&#8377;1,225.00', '&#8377;1,460.00', 'D', 72, 'B', '<b>&#10;(D)&#160;</b><div>The cost of leveling and turfing the square lawn = Rs.13322.50</div><div><div><div>$\\therefore$ Area of the square lawn $=$ Rs. $\\frac{13322.50}{2.50}$</div><div>$$=\\frac{13322.5}{2.5}=5329 \\mathrm{m}^{2}$$<br></div></div><div>$\\therefore$ Side of the square $=\\sqrt{5329}=73 \\mathrm{m}$</div></div><div>Perimeter of a square = 4a<br></div><div>Perimeter of the square lawn = 4 x 73 = 292 m</div><div><div>.\'.The cost of fencing the lawn = 292<span>&#160;x 5 = Rs. 1460</span></div></div>', '', '0', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', 1),
