(1327, 140, 77, 'A fair die is rolled. Find the probability of getting a prime factor of 6', '', 'top', '<font face=\"Arial\" size=\"3\">$$\\frac{2}{3}$$</font><br>', '$$\\frac{1}{3}$$', '$$\\frac{5}{6}$$', '$$\\frac{1}{2}$$', 'B', 77, 'A', '<b>(B)</b>&#160;<div>The faces of a die = 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6&#160;</div><div>Prime factors of 6 are= {2, 3}</div><div>.\'.  n(S) = 6, n(E) = 2&#160;</div><div>&#160;.\'. Probability of getting a prime factor of 6,&#10;&#10;$$P(E)=\\frac{n(E)}{n(S)}=\\frac{2}{6}=\\frac{1}{3}$$</div>', '', '0', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', 1),
