(1378, 142, 58, 'A ramp for unloading a moving truck has an angle of elevation of 30<span>&#730;</span>. If the top of the ramp is 0.9 m above the ground level then find the length of the ramp.', '', 'top', '2 m', '1.5 m', '1.8 m', '1.6 m', 'C', 58, 'B', '<b>(C)&#160;</b><div>&#160;In the figure, Ac is the ramp.&#160;</div><div>Let the length of the ramp be \'l \' m&#160;</div><div>$$\\begin{aligned}&#10;&amp;\\sin 30=\\frac{0.9}{1}\\\\&#10;&amp;\\frac{1}{2}=\\frac{0.9}{1}&#10;\\end{aligned}$$&#160;&#160;</div><div><span>l=0.9 x 2m = 1.8m</span></div><div>&#160;.\'. The length of the ramp = 1.8 m</div>', 'uploads/da593f1e3fb9c019d2d43fa18a64a9e8.jpg', 'top', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', 1),
