(1729, 162, 65, 'If LCM of \"a\" and \"b\" is a and LCM of \"b\" and \"c\" is b. then what is the LCM of \"c\" and \"a\".', '', 'top', 'a', 'b', 'c', 'abc', 'A', 65, 'B', '<b>(A)</b><div>L.C.M of \'a\' and \'b\' = a&#160;<div>&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;a x b = a&#160;</div><div>$$b=\\frac{a}{a}=1$$&#160;</div><div>L.C.M of \'b\' and \'c\' = b</div><div>&#160;$$C=\\frac{b}{b}=1$$</div><div>.\'. L.C.M. of \'c&#8217; and \'a\'  =  1 x a = a</div></div>', '', '0', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', '2020-03-17 00:00:00', 1);
